lines.text: Some think that all persons living in the west coast are crazy, but this doesn't bother people of the west coast. They are too busy enjoying it.

It's been said that Canada is the oldest underdeveloped country in the world. That She is the size of China with the population of Iran. That She has the cultural development of Afghanistan, the economic structure of the Congo, and the climate of Siberia. But the people who say these things, are Canadians. The rest of the world seems to like Her. She is generally good natured, and from what we have been able to see of Her, She looks Just Fine.
